<br>
First I have NEVER refused to summon focus items for people or have even accepted payment for them, and will NEVER . I Dont care if you put 2K in the trade window and click trade...I will cancel it. Unless its summoned pp I can not in good conscious accept it for summoned gear...but<br>
<br>
If you are going on a raid or we are getting a group together, that is the time to ask, not 30 mins. into the group/raid. I mem all 5 spells (4 atm...FIX MY BAUBLE!) and summon a full set for me, then as people as, I hand them mine and summon a new one...when I am done and no one ese asks, I un mem the spells and put my battle spells in. After that you will get attitude that I know have to unmem 3 - 5 spelss cast new items and remem the spells again, usually as the puller is pulling...therefore missing out on any chace of being part of the fun. You will notice that when I am in nexus or baazar sitting doing nothing ill summon up anything in the world for you with out comment, but when I say &quot;Thank you for shopping at Bray-mart...I am usually ticked about the constant memming and un memming of spells. <p>Braydin Firebehli<BR>
